lead_paragraph: The teenagers at the top of women's golf, Lydia Ko and Brooke Henderson, form a mutual admiration society and a burgeoning rivalry that will feature at the U.S. Women's Open starting on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Teen Queens of Women's Golf to Duel at U.S. Women's Open
